\v 41 Xqui⁴ no¹ qui³ xi³jcha¹-le⁴ ya⁴ Jerusalén, cˀia⁴ nca³ sˀoi¹ pa²xco⁴.  
\v 42 Cˀia⁴ nca³ Jesús tjin¹-le⁴ te³jao² no¹, nca³tsˀi³ qui³mi³ ya⁴ Jerusalén jo³-sˀin² coan³nca³-le⁴ sˀoi¹ pa²xco⁴.  
\v 43 Cˀia⁴ nca³ qui³si³cji³tjo³son² ni⁴čhjin³-le⁴, qui³-ni³ xi³jcha¹-le⁴, tsa³cˀe²jna³ ti³ xi³ Jesús ˀmi² ya⁴ Jerusalén, to⁴nca³ li²coi³ tjin¹jin³-le⁴ xi³jcha¹-le⁴.  
\v 44 Xi³jcha¹-le⁴ qui³si³cja³ˀai³tsjen³ nca³ Jesús ti¹jna³jin³-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ tjio¹fi², tsa³cˀe²ma³ ya⁴ ntia⁴² jnco³ ni⁴čhjin³. Cˀoa⁴ tsa³ca¹sjai³tˀa³-le⁴ xi¹ncjin¹ cao⁴ xi³ ve³xcon³.  
