\v 18 Je² Espíritu-le⁴ Nai³-na¹ ti¹jna³cao⁴-na³, nca⁴ qui³tsjon²jon³-na³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ xa¹ nca³ an³ nchja²ya³jin³-le⁴ xi³ yo⁴ma⁴ je² en¹nta³. Qui³si³ca³sen¹-na³ nca³ si³nta³ya³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ cjoa⁴ˀaon³ tjio¹jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-le⁴, nca³ coi³nchja²ya³jin³-le⁴ preso nca³ coa⁴tio⁴ntai¹, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ je² xi³ xca⁴ cjoan³ nca³ coan⁴tsen³-le⁴ xcon⁴, nca³ si³cˀe¹yo³ntai¹ xi³ qui³ni²quin²ˀaon³.  
