\v 36 Tsa³cˀe¹tsˀoa³-le⁴ Jesús jnco³ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseo nca³ coa⁴cjen⁴cao⁴. Ja³ˀa³sˀen³ ya⁴³ ntˀia³-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ fariseo, tsa³cˀe²jna³tˀa³ ya¹mi²xa⁴.  
