\v 39 Tˀin³ ni³ˀya³-li⁴, tˀe²-lai⁴ na⁴jmi¹ jo³ nca³ tjin¹ cjoa⁴nta³ xi³ ca²sˀin¹ xi³ tˀa³tsi⁴. Cˀoa⁴ qui³ cho⁴ta⁴-ve⁴, qui³si³nca³son² en¹ nca³qui³jnta² na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹-ve⁴ jo³ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴xcon¹ xi³ qui³sˀin³ Jesús xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴. 
\s1 Tso²ti³-le⁴ Jairo 
