\v 43 Nca³tsˀi³ to⁴coan³xcon¹-le⁴ je² cjoa⁴je³ya³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹. Tjen⁴ cji³ma³xcon¹-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ xi³ qui³sˀin³, Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴:  
