\v 27 Cho⁴ta⁴chji⁴ne⁴ qui³tso²: Ca²ta³ma³tsjoa³chai³ je² Nai³li⁴ Ni³na¹-li⁴. Ca²ta³ma³tsjoa³cha³-ni³ nca³yi³je³ ni⁴ma⁴-li⁴, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴tsjoa³-li⁴, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ nca³yi³je³ nca³nˀion¹-li⁴, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴fa³ˀai³tsjen³-li⁴. Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ ca²ta³ma³tsjoa³chai³ nca³tsˀi³ xi³cˀa³ jo³-ni³ tsa² ti⁴ji³-ni³.  
