\v 35 Xi³ coan³ nchaon³-ni³ tsˀa³sje³ jao² taon⁴vi²xo⁴, qui³tsjoa³-le⁴ nai³-le⁴ ntˀia³, cˀoa⁴qui³tso²-le⁴: Ti⁴coi²nta⁴-la²nai¹³, cˀoa⁴ nca³yi³je³ xi³ si⁴cje³-sai³, an³ cˀoe³chji¹-le²³ cˀia⁴ nca³ cjoe²ˀe⁴-nia³.  
\v 36 Jo¹ si³, ˀya¹-ni³ xi³ jan² ma³-ni³, xi³ mi²yo⁴-le⁴ je²-ve⁴ xi³ qui³sca³ya³ ntsja³ je² che¹-ve⁴.  
\v 37 Cˀoa⁴ je² qui³tso²: Je² xi³ coan³ma⁴que³. Jesús qui³tso²: Tˀin³, cˀoa⁴tˀiain⁴ nta³ tsa² ji³. 
\s1 Jesús ji³cho²con³-le⁴ María cao⁴ Marta 
