\v 17 Cˀia⁴ nca³ ti¹tso² je² cjoa⁴-vi⁴, coan³soa³-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³ xi³ co²ntran⁴-le⁴, to⁴nca³ nca³tsˀi³ cho⁴ta⁴ncjin² coan³tsjoa³-le⁴ nca³yi³je³ cjoa⁴ xi³ je³ya³ xi³ Jesús qui³sˀin³. 
\s1 Cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ cˀoa⁴cjoan³ ˀnti¹na⁴xin⁴ xi³ tsˀe⁴ mostaza 
