\p  
\v 34 Jerusalén, Jerusalén, ji³ xi³ ni²cˀain³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ nchja⁴ya³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹, cˀoa⁴ la⁴jao⁴ ni²cˀen³-ni³ je² xi³ ni²ca³sen¹con³-li² nca³ ji³. Jo¹-la²na¹ tjin¹ cˀa³ nca³ coan³me³-na³ nca³ tsa³cˀe³xcoa¹³ ˀnti¹xti³-li⁴ jo³-ni³ tsa² xa⁴ˀnta⁴ xi³ vˀe¹nqui³jnca³ ˀnti¹-le⁴, to⁴nca³ coan³cai³-li².  
