\r (Mt. 22:41-46; Mr. 12:35-37) 
\p  
\v 41 Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴: Jo¹-sˀin²ˀni³ nca³ tso² nca³ Cristo ˀnti¹-le⁴ David.  
\v 42 Ti⁴je²-ni³ David tso² ya⁴ libro Salmos: Je² Nai³-na¹ qui³tso²-le⁴ Nai³-na⁴: Ti⁴jna³tˀa³-nai¹³ nca³qui²xi⁴-na⁴,  
\v 43 sa³ˀnta³ si³cˀe¹yoa³ co²ntran⁴-li⁴ ya⁴nqui³ ntso⁴coi³, jo³-ni³ tsa² ya¹ jña³ ncha³son² ntso⁴coi³.  
\v 44 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² David Nai³-na⁴ tso²-le⁴. Jo¹-sˀin²ˀni³ nca³ ˀnti¹-le⁴ ma³-le⁴. 
