\r (Mt. 23:1-36; Mr. 12:38-40; Lc. 11:37-54) 
\p  
\v 45 Tjio¹nčhˀoe¹-le⁴ nca³tsˀi³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹, cˀia⁴ nca³ Jesús cˀoa⁴qui³tso²-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴:  
\v 46 Ti⁴coi²nta⁴-lao⁴³ yao³-no³ cho⁴ta⁴ scribano xi³ tsjoa³-le⁴ vˀa³mjen³ cao⁴ na³jño³jnčho³, cˀoa⁴ tsjoa³-le⁴ nca³ cho⁴ta⁴ si⁴²ti²ˀnta³-le⁴ ya⁴ nti⁴tsin⁴-ve⁴, cˀoa⁴ me³-le⁴ je² ya¹xi²le⁴ xi³ ti¹tjon² ya⁴³ ntˀia³ sinagoga, cˀoa⁴ je² ˀnte³ xi³ ti¹tjon² ya⁴ jña³ cjen²sˀoi¹.  
\v 47 Xi³ fa³yo³ntjai² ntˀia³-le⁴ ya¹nchjin¹ xi³ cˀen³ xˀin⁴-le⁴. To⁴chji³ne³-ni¹ tse³² vˀe¹tsˀoa³. Je² xi³ cˀoa⁴cjoan³ nqui²sa⁴ tse³ cjoa⁴ñˀain³ sˀe⁴-le⁴. 
\c 21  
\s1 ˀnti¹qui⁴cha⁴si³ne² tsa³qui³ncha¹ ˀnti¹chjon⁴² 
