\p  
\v 1 Cˀia⁴ Jesús qui³sco²tsen³-le⁴, tsa³ve³ cho⁴ta⁴nchi⁴na¹ nca³ tsa³qui³ncha¹ taon⁴-le⁴ ya⁴³ ca²xa⁴-le⁴ yo⁴nco⁴.  
\v 2 Cˀoa⁴-ti⁴ tsa³ve³ jnco³ ˀnti¹chjon⁴² xi³ yo⁴ma⁴, xi³ je³cˀen³ xˀin⁴-le⁴. ˀnti¹qui⁴cha⁴si³ne² tsa³qui³ncha¹ ya⁴-ve⁴.  
\v 3 Jesús qui³tso²: Xi³ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴ xi³ xin³-no³ nca³ je² chjon⁴²-vi⁴ xi³ yo⁴ma⁴, xi³ je³cˀen³ xˀin⁴-le⁴, nqui²sa⁴ tse³ tsa³qui³ncha¹ cao⁴-ni³ tsa² nca³tsˀi³.  
\v 4 Nca³tsˀi³ je²-vi⁴ to⁴ca²tsjoa¹cjoa⁴tjao²-le⁴ Ni³na¹ xi³ njen³nqui³-le⁴, to⁴nca³ je²-vi⁴ nta³ tsa² yo⁴ma⁴ tsa³qui³ncha¹ nca³yi³je³ xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ xi³ cjen². 
\s1 Jtsao⁴nqui³ yo⁴nco⁴, choa⁴xcon¹ xi³ nčhoa¹-ni³ 
\r (Mt. 24:1-28; Mr. 13:1-23) 
\p  
\v 5 Cˀoa⁴ tjin¹ cˀa³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ qui³nchja⁴ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ yo⁴nco⁴, nca³ coan³nˀion¹tˀa³ la⁴jao⁴ xi³ na³sca¹cjoan³, cˀoa⁴ cao⁴ cjoa⁴tjao² xi³ tsa³cˀai²-le⁴. Jesús qui³tso²-le⁴:  
\v 6 Tˀa³tsˀe⁴ je² cjoa⁴ xi³ ˀyao³-vi⁴, cjoa⁴ˀai¹ ni⁴čhjin³ nca³ tsi² ti⁴sa⁴tio²son²-ni³le⁴ xi¹ncjin¹ la⁴jao⁴, cˀoa⁴ jtsao⁴nqui³ nca³yi³je³.  
\v 7 Qui³tsi²na³nqui³-le⁴: Maestro, cˀia¹-ni³ve⁴ nca³ cˀoa⁴coan⁴ je² cjoa⁴-vi⁴. Jme¹ choa⁴ xi³ sˀe⁴ cˀia⁴ nca³ me³coan⁴jnco³ nca³yi³je³ je² cjoa⁴-vi⁴.  
\v 8 Cˀia⁴ qui³tso² Jesús: Cho¹tsaon³ jme¹-ni³ nca³ tsi² coai⁴cao⁴-si¹ni³no³ ntia⁴²tˀa³xin², nca⁴ cjai¹ ncjin² cjoa⁴ˀai¹ cao⁴ jan³ˀain¹-na⁴, coi⁴tso⁴: An³ nia¹³ Cristo. Cˀoa⁴ coi⁴tso⁴-sa³: Ni⁴čhjin³ ti¹jna³čhian³-ni¹. A³li² ma³nquin¹tjen⁴nqui³-jin²lao⁴³ nca³ je².  
\v 9 Cˀia⁴ nca³ coi⁴no²ˀya²-lao⁴³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴jchan¹ cao⁴ cjoa⁴si³, a³li² vi³jcon³-jion²³, nca⁴ ma³chjen¹-ni¹ nca³ ti¹tjon² cˀoa⁴coan⁴ cjoa⁴ je²-vi⁴. To⁴nca³ li²coi³ nti⁴ton⁴ cjoe⁴tˀa³.  
\v 10 Cˀia⁴ qui³tso²-le⁴ˀni³: Coi⁴so¹tjen⁴ne² na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹ co²ntran⁴-le⁴ xi³ cja⁴ˀai¹ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹, cˀoa⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³ co²ntran⁴-le⁴ cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³.  
\v 11 Cˀoa⁴ cjoa⁴ˀa² chaon¹xcon¹, cˀoa⁴ cjai¹ ncjin² ˀnte³ coan⁴ cji³nčha¹ chˀin³ˀvi³. Cˀoa⁴ sˀe⁴ cjoa⁴xcon¹, cˀoa⁴ cjai¹ tse³ choa⁴xcon¹ xi³ nčhoa¹-ni³ ncˀa³jmi³.  
\v 12 To⁴nca³ to⁴nqui³-ni³ nca³yi³je³ je² cjoa⁴-vi⁴, tsoa⁴-ni³no³ cao⁴ ntsja³, chˀao³ coai⁴tjen⁴nqui³-no³, sca⁴ni²tˀa³-no³ ntˀia³ sinagoga, cˀoa⁴ sca⁴ni²sˀen³-no³ nto⁴ya¹. Coai⁴cao⁴-no³ nqui³xcon⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ti¹tjon², cˀoa⁴ nqui³xcon⁴ gobierno xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ jan³ˀain¹-na⁴.  
\v 13 Je²-vi⁴ cˀoa⁴coan⁴-no³ nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² cˀoao⁴³ en¹-no³.  
\v 14 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tˀao²³-to³con²³, nca³ tsi² to⁴nqui³-ni³ ni²cja³ˀai³tsjaon³ jme³ xi³ coi⁴xon¹³.  
\v 15 Nca⁴ an³ tsjoa³-no³ en¹ cao⁴ cjoa⁴ncjin²to³con² xi³ tsi² tsa² coi³ coan⁴-le⁴ cˀoe⁴²tˀa³-no³, ni⁴cˀoe⁴²cjao²ˀa²cao⁴-jin²no³ nca³tsˀi³ xi³ co²ntran⁴ coai⁴-no³.  
\v 16 Sca⁴ni²tˀa³-no³, nta³ tsa² nˀai³-no³ cao⁴ ntsˀao³ cao⁴ xi²nquio⁴³ cao⁴ mi²yo⁴-no³. Cˀoa⁴ si⁴²cˀen³cˀa³-no³ nca³ jon².  
\v 17 Coan⁴jti³que³-no³ nca³tsˀi³ xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀan⁴.  
\v 18 To⁴nca³ ni⁴jnco³-jin² ntsja⁴-le⁴ jco³ cha⁴.  
\v 19 Xi³ to⁴tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴tse³jta³-no³ si⁴qui³njaon³ cjoa⁴vi³jna³chon³-no³.  
\v 20 Cˀia⁴ nca³ jchao⁴³ Jerusalén, nca³ tjio¹chjoa²ntai³-le⁴ so³nta²do⁴, jchao⁴³-ˀni³ nca³ coi⁴xo⁴ya³ xi¹ti¹.  
\v 21 Cˀia⁴ je² cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ tjio¹ ya⁴ Judea, ca²ta³ma³nca³ ya⁴ jin³jña¹, cˀoa⁴ je² xi³ tjio¹ nca³va³sen³-le⁴ Jerusalén, cˀoa⁴²-ti⁴ ca²ta³fi²xin², cˀoa⁴ je² xi³ ya⁴ tjio¹ nqui³chao³, a³li² ya⁴ fa³ˀa³sˀen³jin³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹.  
